Package org.actioncontroller.meta

Interface HttpParameterMapperFactory<ANNOTATION extends Annotation>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AnnotationFactory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientCertificate.MapperFactory, ContentBody.ParameterMapperFactory, ContextUrl.MapperFactory, HttpHeader.Mapper, IfModifiedSince.Mapper, JsonBody.MapperFactory, LastModified.Mapper, PathParam.MapperFactory, QueryString.ParameterMapperFactory, RequestParam.ClientIpParameterMapperFactory, RequestParam.MapperFactory, RequestParam.RemoteUserParameterMapperFactory, ServletUrl.MapperFactory, SessionParameter.MapperFactory, UnencryptedCookie.Factory, UnencryptedJsonCookie.MapperFactory, UserPrincipal.MapperFactory
    public interface HttpParameterMapperFactory<ANNOTATION extends Annotation>
extends AnnotationFactory
    Implementations of this interface should be annotated on annotations used to convert HTTP requests into method invocation arguments, such as RequestParam, PathParam and UnencryptedCookie
